products.name: IPhone 12 Pro
products.description: Best iPhone ever features the powerful A14 Bionic, all-new design with Ceramic Shield, pro camera system, LiDAR Scanner, and the biggest Super Retina XDR display ever on an iPhone.

products.name: Samsung S21 Ultra
products.description: The Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra is the headliner of the S21 series. It's the first S series phone to support Samsung's S Pen. Specifications are top-notch including Snapdragon 888 chipset, 5G capability, up to 16gigs of RAM, and 512GB of storage.

products.name: Asus Rog Phone 5
products.description: Play to the max with ROG Phone 5, the gaming phone that takes no prisoners. Powered to win by the latest Qualcomm Snapdragon 888 5G Mobile Platform, this futuristic wonder packs an unbelievably responsive 144 Hz / 1 ms display, a monster 6000 mAh1 battery system, massively upgraded AirTrigger 5 game controls, and our iconic GameFX audio system.

products.name: Poco X4 GT
products.description: The POCO X4 GT is a budget-friendly smartphone that offers a great value for the price. It has a large 6.67-inch IPS 144Hz display and a powerful Mediatek Dimensity 8100 processor. Plus, it comes with a triple camera setup that includes a 108 MP main sensor. The battery life is also impressive, with the phone lasting for more than 24 hours on a single charge.

products.name: Xiaomi Mi 12
products.description: The Xiaomi 12 comes with 6.73-inch AMOLED display with 120Hz refresh rate and Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Gen 1 processor. Specs also include 4600mAh battery with 120W charging speed combined with 50W wireless charging, Triple camera setup on the back with 50MP main sensor and 32MP selfie camera on the front
